*sendRowCol.wcChildren:		send_msg_btn, clear_msg_btn, close_msg_btn

*send_msg_btn.wcConstructor:	XmCreatePushButtonGadget
*send_msg_btn.wcCallback:	SaveHandleCB ( w_send_msg_btn )
*send_msg_btn.activateCallback:	olc_send_msg ()

*clear_msg_btn.wcConstructor:	XmCreatePushButtonGadget
*clear_msg_btn.wcCallback:	SaveHandleCB ( w_clear_msg_btn )
