*close_msg_btn.wcConstructor:	XmCreatePushButtonGadget
*close_msg_btn.wcCallback:	SaveHandleCB ( w_close_msg_btn )
*close_msg_btn.activateCallback:	olc_close_msg ()

*send_frame.wcConstructor:	XmCreateFrame
